  <brief_title>Sevoflurane Decreases the Risk of Postoperative Delirium After Cerebral Hypoxemia During Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Sevoflurane-based Volatile Induction and Maintenance of Anaesthesia (VIMA) Strategy Decreases the Risk of Postoperative Delirium in Elderly Patients With Registered Cerebral Hypoxemia Episodes During General Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
